name: Animarum
description: Animarum - I died. The tide pushes me over, I can only see some others like me.  Our light extinguishes and tries to scape.  I follow them, but there is no place to go. I don´t know who I am, I don´t know if I exist anymore. //////  Animarum - He muerto, la marea me empuja, solo veo a algunos como yo, nuestra luz se opaca intenta escapar, yo los sigo pero no hay a donde ir, ya no se que soy, ya no se si existo.
